attributes.Long form description: The student is to assemble the furniture. The student starts to align the legs to the tables's shelf and tighten the hex socket heads with the allen wrench. The student grabs the furniture and stands it. Then he aligns the table's top and inserts the hex socket heads to keeps it stable. Finally the student uses the allen wrench to tighten the table's top.

attributes.Transcription: We'll now assemble the shelf from Ikea, so please go ahead.

attributes.Action sentence: The student assembles the first leg on the table.
The student assembles the second leg of the table.
The student assembles the third leg on the shelf.
The student assembles the fourth leg of the table.
The student assembles the top table with the furniture.
The student screws the top table onto the furniture.
